exp = get_branin_experiment()
parameters = [RangeParameter(name='x1', parameter_type=ParameterType.FLOAT,
    lower=1, upper=3, log_scale=True), RangeParameter(name='x2',
    parameter_type=ParameterType.FLOAT, lower=1, upper=3, log_scale=True)]
gpei = TorchModelBridge(experiment=exp, data=exp.fetch_data(), search_space
    =SearchSpace(parameters=parameters), model=BotorchModel(), transforms=[
    Log], torch_dtype=torch.double)
transformed = gpei._transform_callback([1.2, 2.5])
self.assertTrue(np.allclose(transformed, [1.2, 2.5]))
